data.description: *SELLER OFFERING $10,000 CREDIT* Introducing your dream 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom villa in The Villages' exclusive 55+ community! With over 1,600 sqft of spacious living, this charming home sits on a large, fenced corner lot that is perfect for dog owners, offering both privacy and serenity. Situated perfectly near Sumter Landing, the Bonita neighborhood pool and recreation center, Havana Championship Golf & Country Club, Seabreeze Recreation Center, Bacall & Bogart Executive Golf Courses, and the Bacall Recreation Center, you'll have endless options for leisure and entertainment right at your doorstep. This beautiful villa boasts a modern and open floor plan, making it perfect for gatherings and everyday living. The well-appointed kitchen features traditional appliances and ample storage, while the living area is flooded with natural light. Step outside to your private oasis – the spacious, fenced backyard, where you can enjoy the Florida sunshine or host barbecues with friends. This villa truly offers the best of The Villages' lifestyle, combining comfort, convenience, and community. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to live in one of the most sought-after 55+ communities in Florida. Schedule a viewing today and make this villa your new home!
